Name: Cave Explorer
About the game: Cave Explorer will allow you to become a gem hunter who, in pursuit of another sapphire, descends deep underground into ancient caves. The locals are not very friendly and will tend to dine with you. Watch out for them and the fire on your way to victory! Can you get to the last level? Peculiarities: - Nice graphics - Achievements - Nice soundtrack by Ozzed
